thread.title: Spectre and Meltdown aren't hurting Intel's profits yet

title: Spectre and Meltdown aren't hurting Intel's profits yet
text:
Spectre and Meltdown aren't hurting Intel's profits yet Thursday, January 25, 2018 - 01:54 
Intel on Thursday gave a bullish forecast and blew past Wall Street profit and revenue expectations for the fourth quarter, but it warned of possible fallout from the chip security flaws.
